{"tid":1564433,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（913人鏈914天水圍915維園）唱歌冇問題，屌唱歌都冇問題，但淨唱歌/淨屌唱歌就有問題","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T00:11:02.000Z","uid":94502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f5234b5ae0c7837bedc13c2ec9a636ddda895b","tid":1564433,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"唱歌冇問題，掛住唱歌唱到唔記得主線，或者唱完當自己做左嘢就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外，所有嘢第一次都係最震撼，做得太多就會膠化/畀人捉到路，唱歌如是，圍狗屋如是，街坊撚狗如是，etc. 既然我地已經establish左有咁多唔同行動可以揀，點樣唔好畀人捉到路就係be water嘅主軸<br />\n屌唱歌嘅人，14失敗唔係因為唱歌，係因為篤灰割蓆互屌，講完唱歌點點點之後唔該推下行動post，同埋唔好成日屌人唔明云伯乜乜物物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />票同支持都唔係屌返黎嘅<br />\n<br />\n最後推下主線任，大家中秋快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120e77ec1cf09a0ca5538e675bffdd9f42a50f37","tid":1564433,"uid":251769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REHv0jX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREHv0jX.png&h=4961a981&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSVp4MD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSVp4MD.jpg&h=3d25b08e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvwgVTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvwgVTi.jpg&h=88868b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZxWVTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZxWVTj.png&h=651de955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88af84bfa37cb413a7fa6a0698fc96958e66583e","tid":1564433,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QV6Mycc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV6Mycc.jpg&h=35dfaea1&s={SIZE}\" />"}